sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant Storage as BlobStorageService
    participant Domain as PdfDocument
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events
    participant BgJob as Background Job

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/ingest/pdf
    Note right of Client: Multipart: file + metadata JSON

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract file and metadata
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create UploadPdfCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check file type = application/pdf
    Validator->>Validator: Check file size ≤ 100 MB
    Validator->>Validator: Check user storage quota
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>Storage: UploadAsync(file, s3Key)
    Storage->>Storage: Generate S3 path
    Storage->>Storage: Upload to blob storage
    Storage-->>Handler: Upload successful (s3Path)

    Handler->>Domain: PdfDocument.Create(gameId, fileName, fileSize, userId)
    Domain->>Domain: Status = Pending
    Domain->>Domain: UploadedAt = UtcNow
    Domain->>Events: Raise PdfUploadedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(pdfDocument)
    DB-->>Handler: Document saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish PdfUploadedEvent

    Handler->>BgJob: Enqueue extraction job
    BgJob->>BgJob: Schedule ExtractPdfTextCommand

    Handler-->>Mediator: UploadResult
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: UploadResult

    Endpoint-->>Client: 201 Created
    Note left of Client: {documentId, fileName, status: "Pending"}

    Note over BgJob: Background processing
    BgJob->>BgJob: Execute extraction pipeline
    BgJob->>BgJob: 3-stage extraction
    BgJob->>Events: Publish PdfExtractedEvent
